4.2.3 GetAtom, GetBond 
 

 
The  GetAtom  and  GetBond  function return a pointer to a single
OEAtomBase or OEBondBase.  The pointer returned is the first instance in
the molecule of and atom or bond for which the predicate function
( vida infra ) passed into these functions as an argument returns
 true .

  
Thus  mol.GetBond(HasOrder(2))  will return a pointer to the first
double-bond in the molecule.

  

  
          
     
        
